I love crackhouse and i love italy so i created a map that is a hybrid of the 2 and i included 3 bombsites. 2 in the houses and 1 in the underground chambers. the point of this map is for the terrorist to rush the building and the undergound while the cts try to surround or counter attack the terrorists.

Please note* that this is a beta and please dont judge its misalligned textures and some bad lighting I know them all and spent time trying to fix them all, and im just releasing this map early to see if people will like it and to get feed back about what i can change gameplay wise.

THANK YOU

 HOPE YOU LIKE IT
